sequenceDiagram
    participant Orch as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Storage<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant VLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant KServe as KServe Storage<br/>Initializer

    Note over KServe,S3: Initialization Phase (HuggingFace Detector)
    KServe->>S3: Download model files<br/>HTTP/9000<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
    S3-->>KServe: Model artifacts
    KServe->>HF: Mount model at /mnt/models

    Note over Orch,BuiltIn: Flow 1: Built-in Detection (Regex/FileType/Custom)
    Orch->>BuiltIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP/8080 | mTLS (Istio)<br/>Platform auth
    Note right of BuiltIn: Local processing:<br/>regex matching,<br/>file-type parsing,<br/>custom Python execution
    BuiltIn-->>Orch: Detection results<br/>HTTP | mTLS (Istio)

    Note over Orch,HF: Flow 2: HuggingFace Model Inference
    Orch->>HF: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP/8000 | mTLS (Istio)<br/>Platform auth
    Note right of HF: Local PyTorch inference:<br/>SeqClassification,<br/>TokenClassification, or<br/>GraniteForCausalLM
    HF-->>Orch: Classification results<br/>HTTP | mTLS (Istio)

    Note over Orch,VLLM: Flow 3: LLM Judge Evaluation
    Orch->>Judge: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP/8000 | mTLS (Istio)<br/>Platform auth
    Judge->>VLLM: OpenAI-compatible request<br/>HTTP/8080 | No encryption<br/>No auth
    VLLM-->>Judge: LLM evaluation response<br/>HTTP/8080
    Judge-->>Orch: Judge evaluation results<br/>HTTP | mTLS (Istio)
